fields.title: Nostromo
fields.synopsis: Nostromo is a novel by Joseph Conrad published in 1904.
fields.content: Published in 1904. Set in the fictitious South American republic of Costaguana, it is an exploration of the debilitating effects of colonialism, capitalism, and political revolution.

fields.title: Neuromancer
fields.synopsis: Neuromancer is a 1984 science fiction novel by American-Canadian writer William Gibson.

fields.synopsis: Snow Crash is a science fiction novel by American writer Neal Stephenson.

fields.title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
fields.synopsis: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen is a comic book series co-created by writer Alan Moore and artist Kevin O'Neill.
fields.content: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen is a comic book series co-created by writer Alan Moore and artist Kevin O'Neill. It was first published by America's Best Comics, an imprint of Wildstorm, and later under the Vertigo imprint of DC Comics.

fields.title: Watchmen
fields.synopsis: Watchmen is a comic book limited series by writer Alan Moore and artist Dave Gibbons.
fields.content: Watchmen is a comic book limited series by writer Alan Moore and artist Dave Gibbons. It was published by DC Comics in 1986 and 1987, and collected in a single volume edition in 1987.

fields.title: 3 body problem
fields.synopsis: Science fiction novel by the Chinese writer Liu Cixin.
fields.content: 3 body problem is a science fiction novel by the Chinese writer Liu Cixin. It is the first novel of the Remembrance of Earth's Past trilogy, but the last one to be translated into English.
